1
00:00:01,001 --> 00:00:02,085
[Jo] <i>Mel, listen.</i>

2
00:00:02,168 --> 00:00:03,837
<i>Never, ever go back to that house.</i>

3
00:00:03,920 --> 00:00:05,755
<i>Your husband is dangerous!</i>

4
00:00:05,839 --> 00:00:07,298
<i>He could kill you.</i>

5
00:00:09,175 --> 00:00:10,176
<i>You sure you're okay?</i>

6
00:00:10,260 --> 00:00:12,178
<i>Yeah. I'm fine.</i>

7
00:00:12,262 --> 00:00:17,517
[Candelaria] <i>I thought you could</i>
<i>convince Atty. Erica Melendez</i>

8
00:00:17,600 --> 00:00:18,977
<i>to be the guest speaker.</i>

9
00:00:19,060 --> 00:00:20,603
<i>You're so lucky</i>
<i>to have them as your friends.</i>

10
00:00:20,687 --> 00:00:22,605
<i>They're all so successful.</i>

11
00:00:22,689 --> 00:00:26,443
<i>Who's the most dangerous criminal</i>
<i>you've faced, Attorney?</i>

12
00:00:26,526 --> 00:00:27,861
<i>Was it Edong Santiago?</i>

13
00:00:27,944 --> 00:00:30,655
<i>I'll save you from her, bro.</i>

14
00:00:30,739 --> 00:00:34,075
<i>I won't let her ruin and poison your life.</i>

15
00:00:34,159 --> 00:00:36,286
[man] <i>Sir, someone left them for you.</i>

16
00:00:36,369 --> 00:00:40,415
[tense music playing]

17
00:00:41,666 --> 00:00:42,834
[investigator] <i>Ma'am Mel has just left.</i>

18
00:00:42,917 --> 00:00:46,796
<i>She came from a condo here in Manila.</i>
<i>Azure Residences.</i>

19
00:00:46,880 --> 00:00:49,799
