<i>The owner of the gyms.</i>

20
00:00:50,550 --> 00:00:53,136
<i>Lucas, you jog here too?</i>

21
00:00:53,219 --> 00:00:54,888
<i>I just got invited by my friends.</i>

22
00:00:54,971 --> 00:00:56,890
<i>- Nice to see you.</i>
<i>- Nice to see you both.</i>

23
00:01:00,143 --> 00:01:01,269
Bitch!

24
00:01:01,352 --> 00:01:02,562
