28
00:01:08,401 --> 00:01:13,073
[tense music continues]

29
00:01:21,915 --> 00:01:26,878
[music becomes sinister]

30
00:01:27,754 --> 00:01:34,177
[theme music playing]

31
00:02:42,954 --> 00:02:45,248
[indistinct chattering]

32
00:02:45,331 --> 00:02:48,501
- Thank you.
- Thank you.

33
00:02:53,464 --> 00:02:56,301
You know, I really thought
you accepted Beth's invitation.

34
00:02:56,384 --> 00:02:57,427
No.

35
00:02:57,510 --> 00:03:00,013
I came here because I had
something important to tell you.

36
00:03:00,096 --> 00:03:03,558
