[phone ringing]

53
00:03:59,572 --> 00:04:00,531
Hello?

54
00:04:00,615 --> 00:04:01,741
[Edong] <i>Captain.</i>

55
00:04:02,367 --> 00:04:03,868
Your assistant's dead.

56
00:04:03,952 --> 00:04:05,495
[ominous music playing]

57
00:04:05,578 --> 00:04:07,080
Will you be next?

58
