76
00:05:13,980 --> 00:05:18,735
[ominous music resumes]

77
00:05:28,995 --> 00:05:30,955
[glass breaks]

78
00:05:38,212 --> 00:05:41,466
[ominous music continues, fades]

79
00:05:41,549 --> 00:05:42,550
Alice.

80
