243
00:14:34,707 --> 00:14:36,000
Like this, right?!

244
00:14:36,083 --> 00:14:38,544
What other nasty things
did you let him do to you?

245
00:14:39,837 --> 00:14:41,839
- [grunts]
- I already know, Mel!

246
00:14:42,631 --> 00:14:44,133
So don't bother denying it!

247
00:14:44,216 --> 00:14:46,635
You fucking cheated
on me, you fucking slut!

248
00:14:48,554 --> 00:14:52,057
- [grunts]
- [thudding]

249
00:14:54,310 --> 00:14:55,853
[music fades]

250
00:14:57,396 --> 00:14:58,647
I'm going home.

251
00:15:01,859 --> 00:15:03,444
We haven't agreed on anything.

252
00:15:03,527 --> 00:15:05,487
I've already told
you my decision, didn't I?

253
00:15:05,571 --> 00:15:07,323
You're making a huge mistake.

254
00:15:07,406 --> 00:15:08,699
Really, Erica?

255
00:15:08,782 --> 00:15:11,994
Beth, please. Let's just wait for Mel.

256
00:15:12,786 --> 00:15:13,954
[huffs]

257
00:15:14,038 --> 00:15:15,247
Fine, but I'll sit over there.

258
00:15:16,123 --> 00:15:22,171
[tense music playing]

259
00:15:30,679 --> 00:15:32,473
[woman 1] Happy birthday!

260
00:15:32,556 --> 00:15:35,059
- Happy birthday!
- Thank you!

